definitions.definition: A country in North America , located south of the United States , and northwest of Guatemala and Belize from Central America. Official name: United Mexican States .
Ellipsis of Mexico City : the capital city of Mexico .
Ellipsis of the State of Mexico : a state of Mexico . Capital: Toluca .
A municipality of the province of Pampanga , Central Luzon , Philippines . Mexico, Pampanga on Wikipedia
